William Beggs, 54, is known as the Limbs in the Loch killer for raping, murdering and dismembering Barry Wallace, 18, in 1999 .
The teenager's limbs and torso were found in Loch Lomond and his head was dumped in the sea off the Ayrshire coast .
Beggs was described by police as a 'serial killer in the making'
He is serving a life sentence in Saughton Prison, Edinburgh, for the murder .